  <jpcrp_cor:ResearchAndDevelopmentExpensesIncludedInGeneralAndAdministrativeExpensesAndManufacturingCostForCurrentPeriodTextBlock contextRef="CurrentYearDuration">
&lt;p style="margin-left: 12px; text-align: left"&gt;※３　一般管理費に含まれる研究開発費の総額&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="table-layout: fixed; width: 648px"&gt;
